{"tid":2136340,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"見到創之軌跡個開場動畫都幾感動","createTime":"2020-08-02T05:42:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-05T06:01:20.000Z","uid":56731,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"d302676848311fd7cf13a8dbbad8b077787b80d7","tid":2136340,"uid":56731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T05:42:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/LuPkbBSSQF0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FLuPkbBSSQF0&d=aFheyUS8Hi5o9a%2F4VMBAnTH2jDdsOF1PL3r%2FkI4IfR4%3D&h=17d1c94a\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/LuPkbBSSQF0</a><br />\n我唔係咩老fans,閃軌先入坑<br />\n一開始玩閃1真係不得了,過場演出尷尬到呢<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/vvyF2DBNGog?t=1559\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FvvyF2DBNGog%3Ft%3D1559&d=aFheyUS8Hi5o9a%2F4VMBAnTH2jDdsOF1PL3r%2FkI4IfR4%3D&h=57061452\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/vvyF2DBNGog?t=1559</a><br />\n但係都幾中意佢個世界觀,同幾在意佢啲劇情先繼續玩落去<br />\n閃1之後間廠出隻隻game我都有買<br />\n所以就睇住依間廠慢慢進步,一開始model都柒隻手正方形<br />\n之後model開始有正常水平喇,但啲動作繼續都係柒,好尷尬<br />\n到佢舊年出隻Ys9,第一次用motion capture,終於追到上嚟創軌仲話會玩VR<br />\n依隻創之軌跡個開場動畫就可以睇到佢哋嘅自信,全in game model演出本既動畫<br />\n就好似睇緊個學生嘅FYP咁,整咗咁多年學咗咁多年既集大成,就係個開場動畫度"},{"pid":"5e4a20619d318267a62a7b94c213a51961e23c5c","tid":2136340,"uid":54232,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T05:45:02.000Z","msg":"閃1，2係過度期，樓主玩埋空同零碧啦"},{"pid":"9248982ac5d5b53c7545bd9de25518daf8fe5a4a","tid":2136340,"uid":24592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T05:50:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />而家我好擔心會唔會全隻GAME有用MOTION CAPTURE既位只有PV同OP show出黎果少少"},{"pid":"140e21553d6934bbfa09a86f0b95d785aa65e31b","tid":2136340,"uid":129738,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9248982ac5d5b53c7545bd9de25518daf8fe5a4a","tid":2136340,"uid":24592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T05:50:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hk